der, Direct bank to bank Net banking - direct from your bank to our bank, or Direct Cash Deposit to our bank.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Discounts</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3><em>2%&nbsp;discount will be given if you pay us using Debit Cards through a secure payment gateway.&nbsp;</em></h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>5% discount will be given if you pay us using:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Direct Net Banking - direct from your bank account to our bank account, or</li>\r\n	<li>Direct Cash Deposit to our bank account.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h2>Cancellation and&nbsp;Refunds made to you:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>All requests for cancellation of payments made to us&nbsp;have to be placed within 7 days from the date of purchase. Please note that no refunds shall be claimed or will be entertained after&nbsp;7 days from the date of Purchase.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Poraapo.com will always be happy to refund&nbsp;money due to you and see you get out!&nbsp;We do not want unhappy customers with us ever.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Any refunds due by Poraapo.com to you due to a Cancellation of an order&nbsp;will be returned in the following manner:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(i) Credit Card / Debit Card: The credit card / debit card account of the registered User will be credited with the refund amount by Poraapo.com. The refund amount will be credited to your account within the time span stipulated by the bank which has issued the credit card / debit card; or</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(ii) Net Banking: The refund amount will only be returned to the account used by you while placing the order.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(iii) Offline Payment (Cheque, DD, Bank Deposit, Cash at Counter): The refund mount will only be returned in the same way used by you&nbsp;while placing the order.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We may suspend or cancel your registration at our reasonable discretion - but only after addressing all your queries and refunding any amounts due to you.&nbsp;</p>\r\n',1,'2015-04-17 00:00:00','2015-04-23 00:00:00',0,0),(14,5,'Contact','	<div class=\"mar_t page-header pad_0\">\r\n		<h1 id=\"forms\